  "text": "In our previous DFT study, we noticed and analyzed a systematic convergence of C-C bonds and changes in π-electron delocalization in benzene rings upon addition of subsequent 1-8 rings and formation of one-dimensional linear acenes [CITATION_1] . Apart from structural parameters, we noticed regular changes in the HOMO and LUMO values in these systems, as well as a decrease in selected Raman active harmonic frequencies in systematically enlarged cyclacenes [CITATION_2] .",
